# Customer Onboarding Guide

## Step 1: Sign Up
- User signs up on the platform.
- Send welcome email with login instructions.

## Step 2: First Login
- Walkthrough dashboard features.
- Highlight key tools and settings.

## Step 3: FAQ / Help
- Link to knowledge base articles.
- Encourage users to reach out via chat or email.

## Step 4: Follow-up
- Check in after 1 week.
- Gather feedback and provide tips
